==Building locks==
# Open the ''Waterways construction'' toolbar by clicking the [[File:en/Manual html m2cc0c4cd.png]] button.<br/>[[File:en/Dock toolbar.png|frame|none|The Waterways construction toolbar]]
# Click on the ''Build lock'' button [[File:en/Build locks.png]].
# Now find a suitable location for the lock. A lock requires two full flat tiles connected by a single slope.<br/>[[File:en/Building-canals-2.png|frame|none|Suitable lock location.]]
# Click on the slope to build the lock.<br/>[[File:en/Building-canals-3.png|frame|none|The lock.]]
# Repeat steps 3 and 4 to place more locks if necessary.

